      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我注意到三个主要参与者：Clinical Engineer（临床工程师）、Azure Backup Vault（Azure备份保管库）、Workload VM（工作负载虚拟机）。标题定为Module 14 – Soft Delete (Logistics_FleetManagement)可以吗？",
