    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：ClinEng到Azure的配置策略消息，以及Azure到Workload的触发备份作业消息。接下来Workload完成备份后，会把恢复点发送回Azure保管库？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng-Azure: Configure policy",
